data.description: Discover the epitome of custom luxury living in this updated home that offers breathtaking mountain views from its peaceful cul-de-sac location! With captivating curb appeal, this residence welcomes you into an array of custom finishes throughout, setting the stage for a truly exceptional living experience. As you step inside, the main level features a front flex room and a dining room. The heart of the home unfolds into an open living area, beautifully adorned with high-end finishes. The kitchen is a masterpiece, featuring quartz countertops, a kitchen island with seating, and stainless steel appliances that cater to your culinary desires. A sunken living room invites you to unwind by the cozy gas fireplace while enjoying sweeping mountain views. Adjacent, a sitting area boasts large picture windows that frame the picturesque scenery. Sliding glass doors lead to an upstairs deck, a perfect spot for taking in the stunning panorama. Down the hall, you'll find a bedroom and a full bath, offering comfortable accommodations for all. The primary bedroom is a true sanctuary, with an en-suite bath and a private balcony, providing a personal retreat with endless views. The basement level expands your living space, featuring a spacious family room with walk-out access and large windows, ensuring an abundance of natural light. Two additional bedrooms, a 3/4 bath, and a laundry room add convenience to daily living. Unwind and rejuvenate in the 4-person radiant heat sauna, a luxurious feature for relaxation. Outdoor entertaining is a delight with ample space, including a covered patio and a large wood-burning fireplace. A pergola-covered area adds charm to the outdoor oasis, while the backdrop of sweeping mountain views enhances the experience. The home's location is a standout feature, offering easy access to parks, trails, and the natural beauty of the area. Plus, you're just a short drive away from Denver, Golden, and Morrison, ensuring you can enjoy city conveniences!
